articles.title: FIA reintroduces F1 qualifying rule ahead of Japanese GP - Racingnews365.com
articles.description: Race director Niels Wittich has informed the teams of his decision.
articles.content:
FIA race director Niels Wittich has reintroduced the maximum time limit for all Formula 1 qualifying laps ahead of the Japanese Grand Prix.
